{"id": 1434, "genre": 1001, "title": "出去玩一圈回来，什么事情你记得最牢？", "description": "反正印象·XX类的歌舞表演我是一点印象也没有。（题图来自：Léonard Dupond）", "record_count": 3000, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170109104009woagCI39ruKmsPR4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-12T03:00:12Z", "options": [{"id": 153088, "content": "吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869774}, {"id": 153344, "content": "心理，个人觉得美的东西，有必要注意的东西……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903342}, {"id": 153856, "content": "就是自己开心的和不高兴的那些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904759}, {"id": 163072, "content": "有趣的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927355}, {"id": 153089, "content": "美食 地标建筑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901258}, {"id": 153345, "content": "致命的孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763874}, {"id": 153857, "content": "美好而让人心动的瞬间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904760}, {"id": 154369, "content": "ggg", "image": "img/option/option/20170116110104oz8HVbDl6m1OrPCh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906413}, {"id": 160513, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 153090, "content": "回来只在乎照片拍得好不好  在狂p照片吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337545}, {"id": 153346, "content": "当地的风俗人情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901982}, {"id": 157954, "content": "小吃和民风", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914673}, {"id": 160002, "content": "买的衣服和包包还有化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915079}, {"id": 153091, "content": "先拍个照发个朋友圈再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825764}, {"id": 153347, "content": "放空的心情❤️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778373}, {"id": 155907, "content": "钱都去哪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497951}, {"id": 160771, "content": "路上的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922164}, {"id": 171011, "content": "伙食不太好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944095}, {"id": 153092, "content": "吃的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902067}, {"id": 153348, "content": "手机充电器不会忘记带", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903353}, {"id": 153093, "content": "我去过那个地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776242}, {"id": 153605, "content": "那个地方的风景和那个地方人给我的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216021}, {"id": 153861, "content": "表演吧，还有人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863271}, {"id": 153094, "content": "在海边抓螃蟹小鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896752}, {"id": 154118, "content": "五六个老外被坑到假长城上大喊amazing", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896879}, {"id": 160774, "content": "被骗，坑了一笔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922146}, {"id": 153351, "content": "另人眼前一亮的开阔的景观，在脑子里航拍一把", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900170}, {"id": 154119, "content": "被坑的经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895914}, {"id": 157959, "content": "记得人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914703}, {"id": 153096, "content": "难忘的是哪个奋力寻找终究没找到的地方，难忘的是醉人的夜晚遇到了一个很奇怪的人，难忘的是突然下雨改变计划的一天，难忘的其实是身边的人，到底谁跟我走过这些地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902720}, {"id": 153352, "content": "没追上的火车，或是寻找半天的厕所。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 893309}, {"id": 153608, "content": "不要在有风的天气做缆车，吓死了好么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902261}, {"id": 154888, "content": "和谁去过，旅途中的糗事和开心的事，坑我的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907212}, {"id": 159496, "content": "光影，水，空气", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918895}, {"id": 161032, "content": "花过多少钱(｡˘•㉨•˘｡)心疼..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914138}, {"id": 153097, "content": "那个售货员好漂亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686906}, {"id": 153353, "content": "当地人的脸和语言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840071}, {"id": 153609, "content": "路上的风景记得最清楚", "image": "img/option/option/201701131836190LQ4qpsju3AinoSY.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904000}, {"id": 154121, "content": "钱花发那了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896743}, {"id": 161545, "content": "看了什么忘了，就记得吃了什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924717}, {"id": 153098, "content": "必须是食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852189}, {"id": 153354, "content": "意料之外的美好景色或人情温暖。计划性总是比不上某一刻的心动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903381}, {"id": 153355, "content": "那种放松的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903384}, {"id": 153867, "content": "我路上花钱不心痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882930}, {"id": 155147, "content": "热爱旅游\n满足尝试新鲜事物的好奇心\n享受自由自在做自己的当下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908009}, {"id": 153100, "content": "我只记得每次腿超酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848366}, {"id": 153356, "content": "總得丟點東西\n越來越會精簡行李", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903400}, {"id": 154124, "content": "两个人环岛半路摩托没电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905510}, {"id": 156684, "content": "美好的与尴尬的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911890}, {"id": 153101, "content": "金沙江边那一抹云彩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902734}]}